# Appointment form email delivery — Resend (https://resend.com), sent from a
# server-side Vercel function (api/book-appointment.ts). These are NOT
# VITE_-prefixed, so they never ship to the browser bundle.
#
# 1. Create a free Resend account and API key.
# 2. Set RESEND_API_KEY below (and in Vercel → Project → Settings →
#    Environment Variables for production).
# 3. Set CLINIC_NOTIFY_EMAIL to the inbox that should receive requests.
# 4. Optional: verify a sending domain in Resend and set RESEND_FROM_EMAIL —
#    until then, mail sends from Resend's shared sandbox address, which
#    works immediately but has weaker deliverability/branding.
RESEND_API_KEY=re_eS6fWDYP_9siDLkRtwqKYjcfkASppBvxA
CLINIC_NOTIFY_EMAIL=sathyadharsan93@gmail.com
RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=onboarding@resend.dev
